trans-unit.source: CustomContentState enables the ability to navigate through different states of a single piece of source content without reloading the source content for each subsequent navigation.
trans-unit.target: CustomContentState gör möjligheten att navigera i olika tillstånd för en enda typ av källinnehållet utan ladda källinnehållet för varje efterföljande navigering.

trans-unit.source: By default, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> does not store an instance of a content object in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Som standard <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>lagrar inte en instans av ett innehållsobjekt i historik.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: Instead, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> creates a new instance of the content object each time it is navigated to by using navigation history.
trans-unit.target: I stället <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>och skapar en ny instans av innehållsobjektet varje gång den navigeras till med hjälp av historik.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: This behavior is designed to avoid excessive memory consumption when large numbers and large pieces of content are being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Det här beteendet är utformat för att undvika överdriven minnesförbrukning när stora tal och stora delar av innehåll som du navigerar till.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the state of the content is not remembered from one navigation to the next.
trans-unit.target: Därför sparas inte tillståndet för innehållet från en navigering till nästa.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] provides the ability to associate a piece of custom state with the navigation history entry for a piece of content.
trans-unit.target: Dock [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] ger dig möjlighet att koppla en typ av anpassad tillstånd till navigering jobbhistorikposten för en del av innehåll.

trans-unit.source: Custom state that is associated with a navigation history entry must be a class that derives from CustomContentState.
trans-unit.target: Anpassade tillstånd som associeras med en tidigare post för navigering måste vara en klass som härleds från CustomContentState.

trans-unit.source: You associate a CustomContentState object with a navigation history entry by using one of the following techniques: - Calling **AddBackEntry**: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Du associera CustomContentState-objekt med en tidigare post för navigering med någon av följande metoder: - anropa **AddBackEntry**:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - Setting <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName> when one of the following events are raised: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - By implementing <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState> on the class that wants custom state to be associated with it.
trans-unit.target: -Ange <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>när något av följande händelser inträffar:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>– genom att implementera <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState>i klassen som vill anpassade tillstånd och kan inte vara kopplad till den.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If you call the **AddBackEntry** method, you must handle the **Navigating** event or implement <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Om du anropar den **AddBackEntry** metod, måste du hantera den **Navigating** händelse eller implementera <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.IProvideCustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: When the navigation history entry is navigated to, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] checks to see if a custom CustomContentState object is associated with it.
trans-unit.target: När den navigering historikpost navigerat till, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kontrollerar om ett anpassat CustomContentState-objekt är kopplade till den.

trans-unit.source: If so, it calls <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.Replay%2A> to allow the custom CustomContentState object to apply the state it remembered from the previous navigation.
trans-unit.target: Om så är fallet bör det anropar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.Replay%2A>så att det anpassade CustomContentState-objektet att tillämpa tillståndet den lagrade från föregående navigering.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.Replay%2A>

trans-unit.source: A custom CustomContentState class can override <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A> to change the name that appears for the navigation history entry to which the CustomContentState object is associated.
trans-unit.target: En anpassad klass CustomContentState kan åsidosätta <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A>att ändra det namn som visas för den navigering historikpost som CustomContentState-objekt är associerat.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value that <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A> returns is visible from the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] of the various navigators ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: Värdet som <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A>returnerar är synliga från navigeringen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] av olika tidsnavigatörer ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState.JournalEntryName%2A>

trans-unit.source: A class that derives from CustomContentState must be serializable, which means it must at least be augmented with <xref:System.SerializableAttribute>, and optionally implement <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>.
trans-unit.target: En klass som härleds från CustomContentState måste kunna serialiseras, vilket innebär att måste minst förstärkas med <xref:System.SerializableAttribute>, och om du vill implementera <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> </xref:System.SerializableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > When you store information in custom content state, you cannot store any references to the instance of the page for which you are remembering state if don’t want the content to be retained in memory.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > När du lagrar information i anpassade innehåll tillstånd kan inte lagra alla referenser till instansen av sidan som du komma ihåg tillstånd om inte vill att innehållet ska behållas i minnet.

trans-unit.source: This prevents [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] from releasing the page instance, and defeats the purpose of the default navigation history behavior.
trans-unit.target: Detta förhindrar [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] friger page-instansen och motverkar syftet med standardbeteendet navigering historik.

trans-unit.source: If you must do this, consider using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.KeepAlive%2A> instead.
trans-unit.target: Om du måste göra detta måste du använda <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.KeepAlive%2A>i stället.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.KeepAlive%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The name for the content that is stored in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Namnet för det innehåll som lagras i historik.

trans-unit.source: The value of JournalEntryName is displayed from <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref>, and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)] navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Värdet för JournalEntryName visas från <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref>, och [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)] navigering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Entries stored in back and forward navigation history are typically available from the back and forward drop down navigation buttons on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] of the host navigator, including <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Poster som lagras i tillbaka och navigering framåt historik är normalt tillgängliga från föregående och vidarebefordra nedrullningsbara navigeringsknappar i navigeringen till [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] för Navigatören värden, inklusive <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, eller [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: JournalEntryName is the <xref:System.String> value that is displayed in a navigation history drop down list.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntryName är den <xref:System.String>värdet som visas i en navigering historik listruta.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: JournalEntryName does not have to be overridden; if not, the following pieces of data are used to automatically construct a navigation history entry name, in order of precedence: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.Title%2A>.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntryName behöver inte åsidosättas; Om inte följande typer av data används för att automatiskt skapa en navigering tidigare postens namn, i prioritetsordning:- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.Title%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.Title%2A>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.WindowTitle%2A> and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the current page - The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the current page.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.WindowTitle%2A>och [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för den aktuella sidan - den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för den aktuella sidan.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page.WindowTitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.String> name of the content that is stored in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.String>namn på det innehåll som lagras i historik.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Called to reapply state to a piece of content when navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Anropas för att tillämpa tillstånd till en del av innehåll vid navigering.

trans-unit.source: Replay is called when an item in navigation history that has an associated <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object is navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Omsändning anropas när ett objekt i historik som har en associerad <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objektet efter att.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: When deriving from the abstract <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> class, Replay must be overridden, although the override implementation need only call the base Replay method.
trans-unit.target: När den härleds från abstract <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>klass, Replay måste åsidosättas, även om åsidosättning-implementering måste bara att anropa metoden grundläggande repetitionsattacker.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService"></xref> owned by the navigator responsible for the content to which this <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> is being applied.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService"> </xref> ägs av Navigatören ansvarig för innehållet som den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> som används.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"></xref> that specifies how the content to which the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> is being applied was navigated to.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"> </xref> som anger hur innehåll som den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> är tillämpas har navigerat till.
